<item>
            <title>[SPR-2204] Hibernate JPA implementation can not find persistence_1_0.dtd</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2204</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With Hibernate EntityManager, the method org.springframework.orm.jpa.PersistenceUnitReader.validateResource (Line 281) raises an FileNotFoundException for the file persistence_1_0.dtd. The reason is, that this file is located in the package org.hibernate.ejb in the library hibernate-entitymanager.jar.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;With TopLink their is no problem, because their the file is located in the root of library toplink-essentials.jar&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="14326">SPR-2204</key>
            <summary>Hibernate JPA implementation can not find persistence_1_0.dtd</summary>
